# Blueprint

When a plan is discussed or code changes land in this session, update [`docs/BLUEPRINT.md`](docs/BLUEPRINT.md):

- Add or adjust **Decisions** if something material was chosen
- Append a dated **Changelog** entry summarizing what changed
- Keep **Current intent** accurate if the project goal shifted

Do not leave the blueprint stale after meaningful work.
